  LAST DUEL

  While playing, pause the game with <F9> and hold down the <Help>, left
  <Shift> and <1> keys together.   Unpause, and pressing the Function keys
  will take you through the levels, and <F8> will give you 5 lives.



  LAST NINJA

  To get past the dragon at the end of level one, you must stand at the far
  left side of the path just at the beginning of the Dragons rocky lair.
  Throw a smoke bomb and if you are on target the Dragon will fall asleep.
  You can now walk past without getting killed.



  LAST NINJA 2

  To board the helicopter at the end of level 5, you must first allow the
  helicopter to leave the screen, then run to the end of the building and
  jump in the direction that the helicopter went, making sure that you
  completely exit the screen.



  LAST NINJA 3

  According to issue 27 of ZERO magazine (best mag!), to access the cheat
  mode in this game, do the following: Gently moisten the underside of a
  wild hedgehog with warm milk, turn it upside-down and shave its left leg.
  Now place it on the keyboard for infinite lives.  Compilers Note: I don't
  how much good this will do the keyboard, the hedgehog or your sanity, but
  go ahead and try it if you really feel the urge.

  If for some strange reason this fails to work, try typing these codes in
  on the high score table:

  Level 1: SUSS
  Level 2: IMED
  Level 3: URTI
  Level 4: BASD
  Level 5: NOUS
  Level 6: RERO



  LEANDER

  Here are a couple of codes:

  Level 2: ZXFT
  Level 3: LVFT

  Also, after you have typed in the appropriate code, enter the letters
  "LTUS" for infinite lives and the ability to select any weapon using
  function keys <F1> through to <F5>.



  LEATHER GODDESSES OF PHOBOS

  The answer to the Sultan's riddle is "Riddle".  To get past the assassin
  in space, fight him until he is disarmed.  Take his sword and give it
  back to him.  He will then realise that you are a good guy, and that he
  has no chance of winning.  He will then kill himself.



  LEATHERNECK

  While playing, type in "CUTHBERTNECK", then pressing <F3> will make you
  invincible.



  LED STORM

  On the title screen, type "DAVID BROADHURST  WANTS TO CHEAT" (put two
  spaces between the second and third words) for infinite lives.  If this
  doesn't work, then See STRIDER - same cheat.



  LEGEND OF FAERGHIL

  Here are the answers to some of the riddles you'll be asked:

  -- In the Elven Palace

  Q: Who is Findals youngest uncle?
  A: Scagnar

  Q: Who is Findals father?
  A: Findail

  Q: Who is Findals great parent?
  A: Alganor

  -- In the Dragon Servant's Temple

  Q: What lies between myself and my opposite?
  A: And

  -- In the Castle

  Q: What tries to go up, but stops short, has but one foot, and cannot
     walk?
  A: Stairs

  -- In the ruins of Ancient Oracle

  Q: The more it gets, the more it eats, and has it eaten all, it dies.
     What it is?
  A: Fire

  Q: I talk without soul, I hear without ears, I talk without mouth, and
     I'm born in air.  What am I?
  A: Echo

  Q: Two little windows, they have no glass, they stand together like
     flowers in grass.  Two little windows, they show us they world, they
     show us the stars, the forest, the field, the fold.  What could they
     be?
  A: Eyes



  LEGEND OF THE LOST

  Enter the password screen and enter one of these passwords.

     2)  STONES    3)  LADDER    4)  ESCAPE    5)  LAVA   6)  FINALE

  You can now select which level you wish to begin on.



  LEISURE SUIT LARRY

  Press <ALT> and <X> to bypass the proof of age questions.  You can go to
  any location in the game by by hitting <ALT> & <D> and entering (TP).  It
  asks for a location number, so enter a number from 008 to 045.



