  LINE OF FIRE

  When on the joystick select screen, type in "OPERATION FERRET".   This
  should give you infinite lives/energy, but if it doesn't work, try typing
  it with a full stop at the end.  Also, now pressing <0> to <9> allows
  you to skip levels.



