  NARC

  Walk right until you come to the first rubbish bin.  Kneel down and keep
  shooting the bin until it turns blue.  You should now have infinite
  lives.



  NARCO POLICE

  While playing, type in "ABRIR" to open doors, "NOENEMIG" to vaporise all
  the bad guys, "COMENZAR" to bring them back again, "BLAST" to activate
  a smart bomb, and "MUNICON" to top up your ammunition.



  NAVY MOVES (Complete Solution)

  Strange: One source says that the code for level 2 is "786169", and
           another states it to be "2277".

  Here is the complete Solution to the game:

  Right, Down, Right
  Shoot 2nd Official and take his code
  Left, Up
  Enter door
  Right
  Shoot 1st Official and take his code
  Left
  Enter door
  Up, Right, Right, Right, Down, Down, Right, Up
  Enter door
  Down
  Enter "EMERGE" on the computer followed by the 1st Offical's code
  Now enter "STOP MOTOR" and enter 1st Officals code again
  Left, Up, Left, Left
  Enter door
  Up, Right, Right, Right, Right, Down
  Enter door
  Right
  Enter door
  Right
  Enter door
  Right, Down, Down, Left, Left, Left
  Shoot the Transmission Official and take his code
