  OVERLANDER

  A Few Hints:

  * When cruising the highway don't stop shooting.
  * Always choose the highest paid mission.
  * Buy fuel carefully - only enough for that level.
  * After level 1 you MUST buy a leanburner.
  * Try to stay in the middle of the road and travel fast - travelling
    slowly only burns more fuel.
  * Fire bombs are more useful than smart bombs when you learn how to use
    them.
  * Bulletproofing is necessary after level 2.
  * When travelling through the barriers the best speed is 90-120mph.



