  PLAGUE

  First make your score end in a three (by shooting the bubbles).  Then hit
  <P> to pause the game, then hit Escape, then click "No" when asked if you
  want to play again. This takes you to the title screen with the drooling
  barbarian.  Now type the following "kom je illegaal door de plaag dan
  grijpt de jungle command je in de kraag", then hit <Return>.  Border
  should turn green.  Hit fire button to return to game.  Now you have
  infinite lives.  You must do all this on Level 1 before you are killed
  even once.



