  PREDATOR

  If your energy gets on the low side, simply press <F10> to restore it.



  PREDATOR 2

  Pause the game and type in "YOU'RE ONE UGLY MOTHER".  Now restart the
  game and you should have unlimited lives and bullets.  If this doesn't
  work, try typing it without the apostrophe.



  PREHISTORIK

  After killing the strange turtle-like creature on the first level, you
  should come to a screen with two carnivorous fish bouncing up and down
  in the water, as well as four banks.  Do not jump over the first well!
  Jump inside it and you will fall down into a secret room.
  Later on in the first level, look out for a ladder near some water which
  leads up to a platform and an egg.  Climb the ladder, take the egg, then
  go to the left, into the water, and you will find a submarine secret
  room.



  PRINCE OF PERSIA

  While playing, press and hold <Caps Lock> while pressing <L> to skip
  levels.



